oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmy Miller Job No. 38678
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Fairlanes (Musical group : Alabama);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3196) for an order placed by Jimmy Miller for 100 two color window cards for a performance by The Fairlanes at the Armory in Tullahoma on July 30. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
